<function>

access:   public

name: fetchAll

param: string|array, $where, NULL

param: string|array, $order, NULL

param: int, $page, NULL

return: Solar_Sql_Rowset

</function>

Fetches all rows by arbitrary criteria.

* Parameters:

 * string|array //$where//: A Solar_Sql_Select::multiWhere() parameter.

 * string|array //$order//: A Solar_Sql_Select::order() parameter.

 * int //$page//: The page number of rows to fetch.

* Returns Solar_Sql_Rowset